QuestData.Title: Fake Gold for Black Gold
QuestData.Description: Now that the "gold" is ready, I want you to take it up to Khan Blizh. He'll be so overwhelmed, I bet he'll offer to help us setup the drilling rigs. We could use the horsepower.$B$BHaha, get it? Horsepower?
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver the Pallet of "Gold" to Khan Blizh at the Splithoof Heights in Thousand Needles.
QuestData.CompletionText: What's this? That is a lot of gold you have there.
QuestData.RewardText: Just put it down on the ground, $r.
